      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;some-interesting-problems&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  Some interesting problems&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#some-interesting-problems&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xD;&#xA;$$&#xA;\text{For} \; n \geq 2 \; \text{the polynomial} \;&#xA;P_n(x) = x^n + a_{n-1}x^{n-1} + \dots + a_1x + a_0 \;&#xA;\text{has the property that} \;&#xA;P_n(k) = 5k^{n-1} \;&#xA;\text{for} \; k = 1, 2, \dots, n.&#xA;$$$$&#xA;\text{Find an expression for} \; a_{n-1} \; \text{in terms of} \; n.&#xA;$$&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Hint: Consider crafting a polynomial $g(x)$ with roots at 1, 2, 3, &amp;hellip; n.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
